title: #92Noon Nordo in for PA! Micheletti/Zimmer presser/Birk/Wobby/Burns
description: Nordo is in for PA! Pat Micheletti talks hockey, Mike Zimmer holds his weekly presser, Matt Birk makes his regular appearance on the Birk Bit, Wobby swings by for a segment, and Ryan Burns of Gopher Illustrated previews Minnesota's battle in the QuickLane Bowl!
